Laurie Zimmer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laurie_Zimmer 0 Laurie Zimmer (also credited as Laura Fanning) is an American former actress best known for her role as Leigh, the courageous secretary of the besieged police station, in John Carpenter's 1976 action film Assault on Precinct 13.
